    - RetrievalEvaluation(queryId, retrievedCount, relevantCount, precision, recall, f1, mrr, ndcg, latency)
    - SynthesisEvaluation(flowId, factualConsistency, completeness, coherence, technicalAccuracy, overallScore, issues)
    - EmbeddingEvaluation(collectionName, intraCohesion, interSeparation, silhouetteScore, testedPairs, latency)
