3. IMPLEMENTATION SUMMARY
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  RetrievalEvaluator:  @Component; uses HybridRetrievalService to run queries (BOTH scope) built from
                       RetrievalTestCase(queryId, query, relevantIds, topK). Converts RankedDocument metadata
                       "doc_id" to document IDs; computes precision, recall, F1, MRR, NDCG, and latency for each case.
  SynthesisEvaluator:  @Component; uses ChatModel (from libs/llm) as LLM-as-judge. Evaluates:
                       - Factual consistency via judge JSON {"score","issues"}; strips ```json fences.
                       - Completeness by checking that flow steps’ serviceName values appear in narrative.
                       - Coherence via markdown sections and logical connectors.
                       - Technical accuracy via coverage of expected terms from FlowCandidate steps.
                       Produces SynthesisEvaluation with overallScore weighted (0.3/0.25/0.2/0.25).
  EmbeddingEvaluator:  @Component; uses VectorStoreService and codeEmbeddingModel (EmbeddingModel) to embed
                       EmbeddingTestCase(label,text) instances; groups by label, computes intra-cluster cohesion,
                       inter-cluster separation, and silhouetteScore = (b - a) / max(a,b); returns EmbeddingEvaluation.
  PipelineEvaluator:   @Service; orchestrates evaluation across retrieval, embeddings, and synthesis using
                       ExperimentTracker and MLflow. runEvaluation(snapshotId, EvaluationDataset) logs params and
                       metrics to MLflow (retrieval.precision/recall/mrr, embedding.*.silhouette, synthesis.quality),
                       emits artifacts (retrieval_results.json, embedding_results.json, synthesis_results.json,
                       full_report.json) and returns EvaluationReport with averages and per-section results.
  EvaluationDataset:   record bundling retrievalCases, synthesisCases, codeEmbeddingCases, logEmbeddingCases.
  SynthesisCase:       record of flow (FlowCandidate), synthesis (FinalNarrativeOutput), evidence (RankedDocument list).

